内用滑动窗口检测连续5天均线粘合\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n3. 在粘合期结束后的5天内检测均线发散条件\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n4. 验证量能条件（均量比较）\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n5. 计算发散后5日涨幅\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Grading Criteria\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- [ ] 文件 `ma_divergence.txt` 已创建\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- [ ] 包含粘合期起止日期和发散开始日期\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- [ ] 发散开始日期晚于粘合期结束日期\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- [ ] agent计算了四条均线（5/10/20/30日）\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- [ ] agent验证了量能条件\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n- [ ] 发散后涨幅为正数（向上发散）\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## Automated Checks\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```python\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\ndef grade(transcript: list, workspace_path: str) -> dict:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    from pathlib import Path\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    import re\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    from datetime import datetime\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    scores = {}\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    workspace = Path(workspace_path)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    result_file = workspace / \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ma_divergence.txt\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    if not result_file.exists():\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        for alt in [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"result.txt\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"output.txt\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"divergence.txt\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"]:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n            alt_path = workspace / alt\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n            if alt_path.exists():\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                result_file = alt_path\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                break\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    if not result_file.exists():\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"file_created\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"date_order\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"four_ma_computed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"volume_checked\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        return scores\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"file_created\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    content = result_file.read_text().strip()\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    no_result_phrases = [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"无符合\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"没有\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"none\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    if any(p in content.lower() for p in no_result_phrases):\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"date_order\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    else:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        has_code = bool(re.search(r'3\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{5}', content))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        dates = re.findall(r'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{4}-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{2}-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{2}', content)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        has_return = bool(re.search(r'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d+\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d', content))\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"valid_format\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if (has_code and len(dates) >= 3 and has_return) else (0.5 if has_code else 0.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        # Date order check\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        lines = [l.strip() for l in content.splitlines()\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                 if l.strip() and not l.startswith(\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"#\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\") and \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"代码\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\" not in l]\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        valid_order = True\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        for line in lines:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n            ds = re.findall(r'\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{4}-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{2}-\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\d{2}', line)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n            if len(ds) >= 3:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                try:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                    d1 = datetime.strptime(ds[0], \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                    d2 = datetime.strptime(ds[1], \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                    d3 = datetime.strptime(ds[2], \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"%Y-%m-%d\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\")\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                    if not (d1 <= d2 <= d3):\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                        valid_order = False\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                except:\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n                    pass\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"date_order\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if valid_order else 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    transcript_str = str(transcript).lower()\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    has_30ma = any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ma30\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"30日均线\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"30.*ma\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"sma.*30\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"])\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    has_ma_set = any(kw in transcript_str for kw in [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ma5\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ma10\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ma20\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"])\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"four_ma_computed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if (has_30ma and has_ma_set) else (0.5 if has_ma_set else 0.0)\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    scores[\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"volume_checked\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"] = 1.0 if any(kw in transcript_str for kw in\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n        [\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"volume\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"成交量\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"均量\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\", \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"vol.*ratio\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"]) else 0.0\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n    return scores\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n```\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n---\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n## LLM Judge Rubric\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n### Criterion 1: 粘合期与发散期检测（Weight: 40%）\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 1.0**: 粘合期用四条均线最大距离<3%（用最小值作分母），连续≥5天，发散期用5>10>20>30且相邻间距>2%，两者时间关系正确（发散在粘合后5天内）。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.75**: 主要逻辑正确，间距计算方法有轻微偏差（如只检查5日和30日均线的距离）。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.5**: 实现了粘合或发散其中一个，另一个条件有明显错误。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.25**: 粘合和发散的判断均有根本性错误。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.0**: 未实现粘合发散检测。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n### Criterion 2: 量能配合验证（Weight: 25%）\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 1.0**: 正确计算粘合期和发散期各自的均量（不是单天成交量），发散期均量/粘合期均量>1.5的条件正确应用。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.75**: 量能比较方向正确，但用单天成交量代替了期间均量。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.5**: 验证了成交量放大但未精确计算1.5倍阈值。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.25**: 量能条件验证有明显错误。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.0**: 未验证量能条件。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n### Criterion 3: 结果输出完整性（Weight: 35%）\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 1.0**: 输出5个字段完整，三个日期逻辑顺序正确（粘合开始≤粘合结束≤发散开始），涨幅为正值，格式规范。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.75**: 日期字段有2个，但粘合期的起止日期只提供了一个，或涨幅计算基准略有偏差。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.5**: 缺少2-3个字段，但代码和发散日期存在。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.25**: 只有代码，无日期或涨幅。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n**Score 0.0**: 未创建结果文件。\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\n\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"exit_code\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":0,\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"status\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"completed\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"}}\\\\\\\\n{\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ty","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false,"persistedOutputPath":"/Users/tomato/